"use strict";(self.webpackChunksoulmatters_ro=self.webpackChunksoulmatters_ro||[]).push([[3122],{3122:e=>{e.exports=JSON.parse('{"author":"Andra Cozma","date":"2015-01-31T18:12:50.000Z","slug":"paradis-sau-iad","status":"publish","title":"Paradis sau iad?","excerpt":"(Autor: C\u0103t\u0103lina Cornea) Paradis sau iad? Singur \xeen paradis sau \xeempreun\u0103 \xeen iad? Ce a\u021bi alege? C\xe2nd a\u0219teptarea \xeen sf\xe2r\u0219it  ","article":"(Autor: C\u0103t\u0103lina Cornea)\\n\\nParadis sau iad? Singur \xeen paradis sau \xeempreun\u0103 \xeen iad? Ce a\u021bi alege?\\n\\nC\xe2nd a\u0219teptarea \xeen sf\xe2r\u0219it se preface \xeen nop\u021bi petrecute \xeempreun\u0103, c\xe2nd distan\u021ba nu mai e un obstacol, atunci tr\u0103ie\u0219ti un vis. Dar \u0219i co\u0219marurile sunt vise.\\n\\nDragostea nu e dec\xe2t o antitez\u0103, e fericire \u0219i chin, e jertf\u0103 \u0219i \xeemplinire.\\n\\nCredeam c\u0103 raiul e s\u0103 tr\u0103ie\u0219ti cu persoana de care e\u0219ti \xeendr\u0103gostit, credeam c\u0103 totul va fi bine c\xe2nd vom fi \xeempreun\u0103. Dar suntem alunga\u021bi din Eden. Via\u021ba ne love\u0219te. Iar zilele de iubire se prefac \xeen zile de ceart\u0103 \u0219i lacrimi.\\n\\n\u0218i chiar dac\u0103 c\xe2teodata credem c\u0103 nu mai avem r\u0103bdare, dragostea ne d\u0103 puteri. Puteri s\u0103 stingem fl\u0103c\u0103rile, puteri s\u0103 trecem peste pr\u0103pastii.\\n\\nPare mai u\u0219or s\u0103 pleci, s\u0103 \xeel la\u0219i pe el cu problemele lui, dar preferi s\u0103 r\u0103m\xe2i, preferi s\u0103 \xeenfrun\u021bi tot ce se \xeent\xe2mpl\u0103, \xeempreun\u0103. C\u0103ci dac\u0103 pleci, \xee\u021bi va p\u0103rea r\u0103u. Vei regreta mereu c\u0103 l-ai p\u0103r\u0103sit. A\u0219 prefera chinurile \xeempreun\u0103, dec\xe2t regretele de una singur\u0103.\\n\\n\u0218i doar sper c\u0103 vor veni zile mai bune, c\u0103 vom fi din nou pe norul din rai.\\n\\nNu renun\u021b nici azi, nici m\xe2ine! Dragostea va fi scutul meu.\\n\\n\u0218i \xeendr\u0103gosti\u021bii sunt cei ce omoar\u0103 dragostea. \xcendr\u0103gosti\u021bii ce nu pot renun\u021ba la egoism, ce nu pot lupta, ce nu se pot jertfi.\\n\\nDragostea devine o lupt\u0103, cu tine \xeensu\u021bi.\\n\\nDoar \xeen bra\u021bele iubitului/iubitei vei g\u0103si lini\u0219tea, chiar dac\u0103 \xeen jur iadul se dezl\u0103n\u021buie.\\n\\nNu renun\u021ba\u021bi niciodat\u0103 la dragoste, renun\u021ba\u021bi la m\xe2ndrie, renun\u021ba\u021bi la capricii!\\n\\nIubire, ap\u0103r\u0103-m\u0103 de oameni \u0219i de mine, ap\u0103r\u0103-ne pe noi, \xeendr\u0103gosti\u021bii, de distrugere.\\n    ","previous":{"slug":"un-scop","title":"Un scop"},"next":{"slug":"un-om","title":"Un om"}}')}}]);